{"tid":1159823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大快活主席親寫四頁信勸兒子接班：我無逼佢！","createTime":"2019-05-18T04:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T06:04:29.000Z","uid":155412,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a38c66ce96633b67e3d30409dee9ac69c0898748","tid":1159823,"uid":155412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4/330293/%E6%BA%AB%E5%A4%9A%E5%A8%9C%E6%89%8B%E8%A8%98-%E5%A4%A7%E5%BF%AB%E6%B4%BB%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E8%A6%AA%E5%AF%AB%E5%9B%9B%E9%A0%81%E4%BF%A1%E5%8B%B8%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E6%8E%A5%E7%8F%AD-%E6%88%91%E7%84%A1%E9%80%BC%E4%BD%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F330293%2F%25E6%25BA%25AB%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25A8%259C%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A8%2598-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AF%25AB%25E5%259B%259B%25E9%25A0%2581%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%258B%25B8%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%258F%25AD-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2580%25BC%25E4%25BD%25A2&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=de571a30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4/330293/%E6%BA%AB%E5%A4%9A%E5%A8%9C%E6%89%8B%E8%A8%98-%E5%A4%A7%E5%BF%AB%E6%B4%BB%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E8%A6%AA%E5%AF%AB%E5%9B%9B%E9%A0%81%E4%BF%A1%E5%8B%B8%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E6%8E%A5%E7%8F%AD-%E6%88%91%E7%84%A1%E9%80%BC%E4%BD%A2</a><br />\n<br />\n大快活集團（0052）主席兼行政總裁羅開揚今日出席零售高峰會，與兒子羅輝承大談接班經過，指自己早已年過60歲，需要為公司將來打算，於是鼓勵兒子從溫哥華回港接班，笑言「我無逼佢！」<br />\n<br />\n羅開揚是大快活創辦人羅芳祥的兒子，叔父羅騰祥則是大家樂（0341）快餐創辦人。對於外界時有混淆兩間快餐店，羅開揚指，「爸爸先構思整個快餐概念，叔叔再跟住加入，當時大家樂及大快活只得一兩間分店，未曾想過會有競爭。」<br />\n<br />\n手寫信勸兒子回港接班<br />\n<br />\n羅開揚透露，當初並無打算繼承父業，年少時選擇赴美國修讀圖像設計，而父親亦十分開明，讓他自己選擇前路。不過，他笑指自己當年想法非常不切實際，曾經於文革時期，計劃在紐約開一間名為「Cultural Revolution」的餐館。後來，二哥寫信勸他回港，於是他便開始投入家族事業。<br />\n<br />\n羅輝承與父親同樣，走上繼承家族事業的道路，於今年1月加入大快活擔任執行董事。羅輝承透露，與妻子一直定居溫哥華，有天收到父親長達4頁紙的親筆信，希望他回港接手大快活，他短暫回公司工作逾半年，一度與妻子分隔兩地，後來決心回港定居，加入公司輔助父親。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rMDhqv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rMDhqv.png&h=ed8ef8fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f436be8b2c4360c3caf2a9f1b014bcf265d2696","tid":1159823,"uid":94828,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7210de25694875d907a75d1dedd757a68619e2e4","tid":1159823,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"依家先知大家樂同大快活fd底"},{"pid":"3e93438464290cd9494f023ceb0b027b1f530835","tid":1159823,"uid":194415,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7210de25694875d907a75d1dedd757a68619e2e4","tid":1159823,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"依家先知大家樂同大快活fd底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兄弟 ＝ fd？"},{"pid":"e07333c06c68e0c24af308d0d8859679b0c4c163","tid":1159823,"uid":92265,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"7210de25694875d907a75d1dedd757a68619e2e4","tid":1159823,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"依家先知大家樂同大快活fd底"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"親兄弟<br />\n但唔friend"},{"pid":"6deff7911d59bdbbdcb027ae96ce6fc74daa7fe9","tid":1159823,"uid":194877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7210de25694875d907a75d1dedd757a68619e2e4","tid":1159823,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"依家先知大家樂同大快活fd底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"咪自己斷9 估啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bdfe4ec16f88339ff43024c08a07982655ffeb","tid":1159